plot: Irving finds an intriguing book at work. Helly aggressively pursues a meeting with her Outie. Mark attends a funeral with Ms. Selvig.

Burt pays a visit to Macro-data Refinement with Mark and Irving, presenting some pre-release gift totes as gifts along with an invitation for any of them to visit the O and D department. He even provides a map. Irving goes out in search of Burt while Helly returns from an all-nighter in the break room. Burt and Irving visit and Mark finds his own much more detailed map of the grounds. When the others discover it some fevers get raised. Mark destroys the map and Irving finds the brother-in-law's self-help book; a major breach of protocol.—travisammons
